{
  "stem": "3848.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The other four were working, pushing those trees up to the top to put them into the machine to cut for those ties.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I had a pretty good job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was some food because we had coupons to-- to go to a restaurant to eat something, not too much, but just to exist.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had a place to sleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and it was considering, for us, it was luck to be there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "During that time, I was always running to the-- to the railroad station to look for refugees who were coming by.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was looking for my family at all times.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Wherever I was, I always looked into the cars to see if maybe somebody from my city, somebody of my relatives is passing by.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I didn't find anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I-- I met some friends that also were looking for-- for family in the same transports that were passing by Tashkent.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "One day, my uncle, which came back from the front, he was wounded.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And because he was a soldier in the Russian army, taken right away when the war started, and they were defeated.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was full of wounds from the trenches that he was lying, fighting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He came with a group that he had, that wanted to go to the Polish army to sign up to the Polish army, Sikorski army, which was formed at a time in Russia.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The Russian government gave him permission to gather all the Polish people and then go and fight from the English side.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was traveling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He passed by Tashkent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When he walked out, he met this friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he asked whether there were any relatives or any friends from our city of Rovno.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
